{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":806,"text":"Okay, this morning I'm speaking"},{"time":2581,"text":"on the question of corruption."},{"time":5770,"text":"And corruption is defined"},{"time":7930,"text":"as the abuse of a position of trust"},{"time":13666,"text":"for the benefit of yourself -- or, in the case of our context,"},{"time":17306,"text":"your friends, your family or your financiers."},{"time":19929,"text":"Okay? Friends, family and financiers."},{"time":24452,"text":"But we need to understand what we understand about corruption,"},{"time":28467,"text":"and we need to understand that"},{"time":31265,"text":"we have been miseducated about it, and we have to admit that."},{"time":34614,"text":"We have to have the courage to admit that"},{"time":36171,"text":"to start changing how we deal with it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":38616,"text":"The first thing is that the big myth, number one,"},{"time":41539,"text":"is that in fact it's not really a crime."},{"time":43910,"text":"When we get together with friends and family"},{"time":45700,"text":"and we discuss crime in our country,"},{"time":47579,"text":"crime in Belmont or crime in Diego or crime in Marabella,"},{"time":51172,"text":"nobody's speaking about corruption."},{"time":52702,"text":"That's the honest truth."},{"time":54252,"text":"When the Commissioner of Police comes on TV to talk about crime,"},{"time":57289,"text":"he isn't speaking about corruption."},{"time":59299,"text":"And we know for sure when the Minister of National Security"},{"time":61615,"text":"is speaking about crime, he's not talking about corruption either."},{"time":65490,"text":"The point I'm making is that it is a crime."},{"time":68105,"text":"It is an economic crime, because we're involving the looting of taxpayers' money."},{"time":72955,"text":"Public and private corruption is a reality."},{"time":75723,"text":"As somebody who comes from the private sector,"},{"time":77454,"text":"I can tell you there's a massive amount of corruption"},{"time":79850,"text":"in the private sector that has nothing to do with government."},{"time":82629,"text":"The same bribes and backhanders and things that take place under the table,"},{"time":85471,"text":"it all takes place in the private sector."},{"time":87939,"text":"Today, I'm focusing on public sector corruption,"},{"time":91540,"text":"which the private sector also participates in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":94675,"text":"The second important myth to understand --"},{"time":96971,"text":"because we have to destroy these myths,"},{"time":98705,"text":"dismantle them and destroy them and ridicule them --"},{"time":101165,"text":"the second important myth to understand"},{"time":103111,"text":"is the one that says"},{"time":105603,"text":"that in fact corruption is only a small problem --"},{"time":108872,"text":"if it is a problem, it's only a small problem,"},{"time":111202,"text":"that in fact it's only a little 10 or 15 percent,"},{"time":114896,"text":"it's been going on forever, it probably will continue forever,"},{"time":118787,"text":"and there's no point passing any laws, because there's little we can do about it."},{"time":122571,"text":"And I want to demonstrate that that, too,"},{"time":124931,"text":"is a dangerous myth, very dangerous."},{"time":126868,"text":"It's a piece of public mischief."}]},{"cues":[{"time":129289,"text":"And I want to speak a little bit,"},{"time":131883,"text":"take us back about 30 years."},{"time":134131,"text":"We're coming out today from Trinidad and Tobago,"},{"time":136125,"text":"a resource-rich, small Caribbean country,"},{"time":139323,"text":"and in the early 1970s we had a massive increase in the country's wealth,"},{"time":144369,"text":"and that increase was caused by the increase in world oil prices."},{"time":147862,"text":"We call them petrodollars. The treasury was bursting with money."},{"time":150897,"text":"And it's ironic, because"},{"time":154585,"text":"we're standing today in the Central Bank."},{"time":156623,"text":"You see, history's rich in irony."},{"time":158819,"text":"We're standing today in the Central Bank,"},{"time":160641,"text":"and the Central Bank is responsible for a lot of the things I'm going to be speaking about."},{"time":164019,"text":"Okay? We're talking about irresponsibility in public office."},{"time":167344,"text":"We're speaking about the fact that across the terrace,"},{"time":170092,"text":"the next tower is the Ministry of Finance,"},{"time":172131,"text":"and there's a lot of connection with us today,"},{"time":173819,"text":"so we're speaking within your temple today. Okay?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":176669,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":181569,"text":"The first thing I want to talk about is that"},{"time":183811,"text":"when all of this money flowed into our country about 40 years ago,"},{"time":187507,"text":"we embarked, the government of the day embarked"},{"time":189594,"text":"on a series of government-to-government arrangements"},{"time":191704,"text":"to have rapidly develop the country."},{"time":193738,"text":"And some of the largest projects in the country"},{"time":196004,"text":"were being constructed through government-to-government arrangements"},{"time":199202,"text":"with some of the leading countries in the world,"},{"time":201018,"text":"the United States and Britain and France and so on and so on."},{"time":203726,"text":"As I said, even this building we're standing in -- that's one of the ironies --"},{"time":206794,"text":"this building was part of that series of complexes,"},{"time":208478,"text":"what they called the Twin Towers."},{"time":212586,"text":"It became so outrageous, the whole situation,"},{"time":215546,"text":"that in fact a commission of inquiry was appointed,"},{"time":218426,"text":"and it reported in 1982, 30 years ago it reported --"},{"time":222429,"text":"the Ballah Report -- 30 years ago,"},{"time":225178,"text":"and immediately the government-to-government arrangements were stopped."},{"time":229114,"text":"The then-Prime Minister went to Parliament"},{"time":231022,"text":"to give a budget speech, and he said some things that I'll never forget."},{"time":234219,"text":"They went right in here. I was a young man at the time."},{"time":236516,"text":"It went right into my heart."},{"time":237896,"text":"And he said that, in fact — Let me see if this thing works."},{"time":242653,"text":"Are we getting a, yeah?—"},{"time":245130,"text":"That's what he told us."},{"time":247129,"text":"He told us that, in fact,"},{"time":251269,"text":"two out of every three dollars of our petrodollars"},{"time":254191,"text":"that we spent, the taxpayers' money,"},{"time":256575,"text":"was wasted or stolen."},{"time":258659,"text":"So the 10 or 15 percent is pure mischief."},{"time":262702,"text":"As we say, it's a nancy-story. Forget it."},{"time":264811,"text":"That's for little children. We are big people,"},{"time":266506,"text":"and we're trying to deal with what's happening in our society."},{"time":269293,"text":"Okay? This is the size of the problem."},{"time":271438,"text":"Okay? Two thirds of the money stolen or wasted."},{"time":274450,"text":"That was 30 years ago. 1982 was Ballah."}]},{"cues":[{"time":277892,"text":"So what has changed?"},{"time":279951,"text":"I don't like to bring up embarrassing secrets"},{"time":281638,"text":"to an international audience, but I have to."},{"time":284197,"text":"Four months ago, we suffered a constitutional outrage in this country."},{"time":287710,"text":"We call it the Section 34 fiasco, the Section 34 fiasco,"},{"time":292608,"text":"a suspicious piece of law, and I'm going to say it like it is,"},{"time":295254,"text":"a suspicious piece of law"},{"time":296609,"text":"was passed at a suspicious time"},{"time":298752,"text":"to free some suspects. (Laughter)"},{"time":300650,"text":"And it was called, those people are called"},{"time":307383,"text":"the Piarco Airport accused."},{"time":308957,"text":"I'm going to have my own lexicon speaking here today."},{"time":311834,"text":"They are the Piarco Airport accused."},{"time":313661,"text":"It was a constitutional outrage of the first order,"},{"time":316554,"text":"and I have labeled it the Plot to Pervert Parliament."},{"time":320610,"text":"Our highest institution in our country was perverted."},{"time":323709,"text":"We are dealing with perverts here"},{"time":325682,"text":"of an economic and financial nature."},{"time":327404,"text":"Do you get how serious this problem is?"},{"time":329253,"text":"There was massive protest. A lot of us in this room"},{"time":331363,"text":"took part in the protest in different forms."},{"time":334073,"text":"Most importantly, the American embassy complained,"},{"time":336892,"text":"so Parliament was swiftly reconvened,"},{"time":339379,"text":"and the law was reversed, it was repealed."},{"time":341284,"text":"That's the word lawyers use. It was repealed."},{"time":343231,"text":"But the point is"},{"time":346348,"text":"that Parliament was outwitted in the whole course of events,"},{"time":350043,"text":"because what really happened is that,"},{"time":352529,"text":"because of the suspicious passage of that law,"},{"time":355603,"text":"the law was actually passed into effect"},{"time":357924,"text":"on the weekend we celebrated our 50th anniversary of independence,"},{"time":361182,"text":"our jubilee of independence."},{"time":362742,"text":"So that is the kind of outrage of the thing."},{"time":364764,"text":"It was kind of a nasty way to get maturation, but we got it,"},{"time":368175,"text":"because we all understood it,"},{"time":369862,"text":"and for the first time that I could remember,"},{"time":371620,"text":"there were mass protests against this corruption."},{"time":375170,"text":"And that gave me a lot of hope. Okay?"},{"time":377361,"text":"Those of us who are, sometimes you feel like"},{"time":379224,"text":"you're a little bit on your own doing some of this work."},{"time":382593,"text":"That passage of the law and the repeal of the law"},{"time":386041,"text":"fortified the case of the Piarco Airport accused."},{"time":390017,"text":"So it was one of those really superior double bluff kind of things that took place."}]},{"cues":[{"time":394628,"text":"But what were they accused of?"},{"time":396524,"text":"What was it that they were accused of?"},{"time":397627,"text":"I'm being a bit mysterious for those of you out there. What were they accused of?"},{"time":400906,"text":"We were trying to build, or reconstruct largely,"},{"time":403488,"text":"an airport that had grown outdated."},{"time":406090,"text":"The entire project cost about 1.6 billion dollars,"},{"time":409880,"text":"Trinidad and Tobago dollars,"},{"time":412447,"text":"and in fact, we had a lot of bid-rigging"},{"time":415610,"text":"and suspicious activity, corrupt activity took place."},{"time":418797,"text":"And to get an idea of what it consisted of,"},{"time":422887,"text":"and to put it in context in relationship to this whole"},{"time":425767,"text":"second myth about it being no big thing,"},{"time":428200,"text":"we can look at this second slide here."},{"time":430971,"text":"And what we have here -- I am not saying so,"},{"time":434664,"text":"this is the Director of Public Prosecutions in a written statement. He said so."},{"time":439471,"text":"And he's telling us that for the $1.6 billion cost of the project,"},{"time":443945,"text":"one billion dollars has been traced"},{"time":446137,"text":"to offshore bank accounts."},{"time":447900,"text":"One billion dollars of our taxpayers' money"},{"time":450063,"text":"has been located in offshore bank accounts."}]},{"cues":[{"time":453461,"text":"Being the kind of suspicious person I am,"},{"time":455574,"text":"I am outraged at that, and I'm going to pause here,"},{"time":458291,"text":"I'm going to pause now and again and bring in different things."},{"time":460787,"text":"I'm going to pause here and bring in something I saw"},{"time":462601,"text":"in November last year at Wall Street. I was at Zuccotti Park."},{"time":466345,"text":"It was autumn. It was cool. It was damp. It was getting dark."},{"time":470537,"text":"And I was walking around with the protesters"},{"time":472470,"text":"looking at the One Wall Street, Occupy Wall Street movement walking around."},{"time":476763,"text":"And there was a lady with a sign, a very simple sign,"},{"time":479083,"text":"a kind of battered-looking blonde lady,"},{"time":481507,"text":"and the sign was made out of Bristol board, as we say in these parts,"},{"time":484330,"text":"and it was made with a marker."},{"time":486322,"text":"And what it said on that sign hit me right in the center."},{"time":488843,"text":"It said, \"If you're not outraged, you haven't been paying attention.\""},{"time":493250,"text":"If you're not outraged by all of this, you haven't been paying attention."},{"time":496232,"text":"So listen up, because we're getting into even deeper waters."}]},{"cues":[{"time":500363,"text":"My brain started thinking."},{"time":502520,"text":"Well, what if --"},{"time":505411,"text":"because I'm suspicious like that. I read a lot of spy novels and stuff."},{"time":508617,"text":"What if -- (Laughter)"},{"time":510295,"text":"But to make it in these wrongs,"},{"time":512819,"text":"you have to read a lot of spy novels"},{"time":514444,"text":"and follow some of that stuff, right? (Laughter)"},{"time":517011,"text":"But what if this wasn't the first time?"},{"time":521578,"text":"What if this is just the first time"},{"time":524165,"text":"that the so-and-sos had been caught?"},{"time":526500,"text":"What if it had happened before? How would I find out?"},{"time":531626,"text":"Now, the previous two examples I gave"},{"time":534116,"text":"were to do with construction sector corruption, okay?"},{"time":538172,"text":"And I have the privilege at this time"},{"time":540203,"text":"to lead the Joint Consultative Council, which is a not-for-profit."},{"time":543581,"text":"We're at jcc.org.tt, and we have the -- we are the leaders"},{"time":547178,"text":"in the struggle to produce a new public procurement system"},{"time":550404,"text":"about how public money is transacted."},{"time":552564,"text":"So those of you interested in finding out more about it,"},{"time":554769,"text":"or joining us or signing up on any of our petitions, please get involved."}]},{"cues":[{"time":559049,"text":"But I'm going to segue to another thing that relates,"},{"time":561308,"text":"because one of my private campaigns I've been conducting"},{"time":564084,"text":"for over three and a half years"},{"time":566420,"text":"is for transparency and accountability"},{"time":568909,"text":"around the bailout of CL Financial."},{"time":572008,"text":"CL Financial is the Caribbean's largest ever conglomerate, okay?"},{"time":577009,"text":"And without getting into all of the details,"},{"time":579932,"text":"it is said to have collapsed — I'm using my words very carefully —"},{"time":582948,"text":"it's said to have collapsed in January of '09,"},{"time":585775,"text":"which is just coming up to nearly four years."},{"time":589453,"text":"In an unprecedented fit of generosity --"},{"time":592265,"text":"and you have to be very suspicious about these people --"},{"time":594748,"text":"in an unprecedented — and I'm using that word carefully —"},{"time":597379,"text":"unprecedented fit of generosity, the government of the day"},{"time":601263,"text":"signed, made a written commitment, to repay all of the creditors."},{"time":604918,"text":"And I can tell you without fear of contradiction"},{"time":607240,"text":"that hasn't happened anywhere else on the planet."},{"time":610422,"text":"Let's understand, because we lack context."},{"time":612333,"text":"People are telling us it's just like Wall Street. It's not just like Wall Street."},{"time":615338,"text":"Trinidad and Tobago is like a place with different laws of physics or biology or something."},{"time":619827,"text":"It's not just like anywhere. (Applause)"},{"time":624571,"text":"It's not just like anywhere. It's not just like anywhere."},{"time":629725,"text":"Here is here, and out there is out there. Okay?"},{"time":632556,"text":"I'm serious now."},{"time":633886,"text":"Listen. They've had bailouts on Wall Street."},{"time":636869,"text":"They've had bailouts in London."},{"time":638820,"text":"They've had bailouts in Europe."},{"time":640957,"text":"In Africa, they've had bailouts. In Nigeria, six of the major"},{"time":643627,"text":"commercial banks collapsed at the same time as ours, eh?"},{"time":646192,"text":"It's interesting to parallel how the Nigerian experience has --"},{"time":648433,"text":"how they've treated it, and they've treated it"},{"time":650823,"text":"very well compared to us."},{"time":652694,"text":"Nowhere on the planet"},{"time":654626,"text":"have all the creditors been bailed out"},{"time":657332,"text":"in excess of what their statutory entitlements were."},{"time":659624,"text":"Only here. So what was the reason for the generosity?"},{"time":663206,"text":"Is our government that generous? And maybe they are."},{"time":666011,"text":"Let's look at it. Let's look into it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":668027,"text":"So I started digging and writing and so and so on,"},{"time":670795,"text":"and that work can be found, my personal work"},{"time":672607,"text":"can be found at AfraRaymond.com, which is my name."},{"time":675987,"text":"It's a not-for-profit blog that I run."},{"time":678859,"text":"Not as popular as some of the other people, but there you go."},{"time":681383,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":683641,"text":"But the point is that the bitter experience of Section 34,"},{"time":688130,"text":"that plot to pervert Parliament, that bitter experience"},{"time":690587,"text":"that took place in August,"},{"time":693673,"text":"when we were supposed to be celebrating our independence,"},{"time":696571,"text":"going into September, forced me to check myself"},{"time":701235,"text":"and recalculate my bearings,"},{"time":703294,"text":"and to go back into some of the work, some of the stuff I'd written"},{"time":705516,"text":"and some of the exchanges I'd had with the officials"},{"time":707785,"text":"to see what was really what."},{"time":709789,"text":"As we say in Trinidad and Tobago, who is who and what is what?"},{"time":713899,"text":"Okay? We want to try to recalculate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":715723,"text":"And I made a Freedom of Information application"},{"time":718147,"text":"in May this year to the Ministry of Finance."},{"time":722061,"text":"The Ministry of Finance is the next tower over."},{"time":724119,"text":"This is the other context."},{"time":725794,"text":"The Ministry of Finance, we are told,"},{"time":727870,"text":"is subject to the provisions of the Freedom of Information Act."},{"time":731699,"text":"I'm going to take you through a worked example of whether that's really so."},{"time":735003,"text":"The Central Bank in which we stand this morning"},{"time":737891,"text":"is immune from the provisions of the Freedom of Information Act."},{"time":742088,"text":"So in fact, you can't ask them anything,"},{"time":743767,"text":"and they don't have to answer anything."},{"time":745460,"text":"That is the law since 1999."}]},{"cues":[{"time":748282,"text":"So I plunged into this struggle, and I asked four questions."},{"time":751858,"text":"And I'll relate the questions to you in the short form with the reply,"},{"time":755547,"text":"so you could understand, as I said, where we are."},{"time":758162,"text":"Here is not like anywhere else."}]},{"cues":[{"time":759683,"text":"Question number one:"},{"time":762661,"text":"I asked to see the accounts of CL Financial,"},{"time":765251,"text":"and if you can't show me the accounts --"},{"time":767723,"text":"the Minister of Finance is making statements,"},{"time":769688,"text":"passing new laws and giving speeches and so on."},{"time":772303,"text":"What are the figures he's relying on?"},{"time":774594,"text":"It's like that joke: I want whatever he's drinking."},{"time":777214,"text":"And they wrote back and said to me,"},{"time":778813,"text":"well what do you really mean?"},{"time":780524,"text":"So they hit my question with a question."}]},{"cues":[{"time":782915,"text":"Second point: I want to see"},{"time":786036,"text":"who are the creditors of the group who have been repaid?"},{"time":789735,"text":"Let me pause here to point out to you all"},{"time":791739,"text":"that 24 billion dollars of our money has been spent on this."},{"time":795420,"text":"That is about three and a half billion U.S. dollars"},{"time":797819,"text":"coming out of a small -- we used to be resource-rich --"},{"time":801315,"text":"Caribbean country. Okay?"},{"time":803687,"text":"And I asked the question,"},{"time":805235,"text":"who was getting that three and a half billion dollars?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":809381,"text":"And I want to pause again to bring up context,"},{"time":811638,"text":"because context helps us to get clarity understanding this thing."},{"time":815041,"text":"There's a particular individual who is in the government now."},{"time":817611,"text":"The name of the person doesn't matter."},{"time":819331,"text":"And that person made a career"},{"time":821883,"text":"out of using the Freedom of Information Act"},{"time":824244,"text":"to advance his political cause."},{"time":826363,"text":"Okay? His name isn't important."},{"time":829606,"text":"I wouldn't dignify it. I'm on a point."},{"time":831939,"text":"The point is, that person made a career out of using"},{"time":834359,"text":"the Freedom of Information Act to advance his cause."},{"time":837323,"text":"And the most famous case"},{"time":839637,"text":"was what we came to call the Secret Scholarship Scandal,"},{"time":842530,"text":"where in fact there was about 60 million dollars in government money"},{"time":845419,"text":"that had been dispersed in a series of scholarships,"},{"time":848291,"text":"and the scholarships hadn't been advertised, and so and so on and so on."},{"time":851015,"text":"And he was able to get the court, using that act of Parliament,"},{"time":854006,"text":"Freedom of Information Act,"},{"time":855639,"text":"to release the information,"},{"time":857616,"text":"and I thought that was excellent."},{"time":860981,"text":"Fantastic."},{"time":864147,"text":"But you see, the question is this:"},{"time":866097,"text":"If it's right and proper for us to use the Freedom of Information Act"},{"time":870310,"text":"and to use the court"},{"time":874040,"text":"to force a disclosure about 60 million dollars in public money,"},{"time":878782,"text":"it must be right and proper"},{"time":880473,"text":"for us to force a disclosure about 24 billion dollars."},{"time":884614,"text":"You see? But the Ministry of Finance,"},{"time":887202,"text":"the Permanent Secretary of the Ministry of Finance,"},{"time":888804,"text":"wrote me and said to me, that information is exempt too."},{"time":891861,"text":"You see? This is what we're dealing with, okay?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":894850,"text":"The third thing I will tell you"},{"time":896984,"text":"is that I also asked"},{"time":899989,"text":"for the directors of CL Financial,"},{"time":902985,"text":"whether in fact they were making filings under our Integrity in Public Life Act."},{"time":907330,"text":"We have an Integrity in Public Life Act"},{"time":908948,"text":"as part of our framework supposed to safeguard the nation's interest."},{"time":913697,"text":"And public officials are supposed to file"},{"time":915985,"text":"to say what it is they have in terms of assets and liabilities."},{"time":922450,"text":"And of course I've since discovered that they're not filing,"},{"time":924865,"text":"and in fact the Minister of Finance has not even asked them to file."},{"time":927744,"text":"So here we have it. We have a situation where"},{"time":932661,"text":"the basic safeguards of integrity and accountability"},{"time":937555,"text":"and transparency have all been discarded."},{"time":939548,"text":"I've asked the question in the legal and required fashion."},{"time":941792,"text":"It's been ignored."}]},{"cues":[{"time":944280,"text":"The sort of thing that motivated us around Section 34,"},{"time":947455,"text":"we need to continue to work on that. We can't forget it."},{"time":950057,"text":"I have defined this as the single largest expenditure in the country's history."},{"time":953655,"text":"It's also the single largest example"},{"time":956236,"text":"of public corruption according to this equation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":961248,"text":"And this is my reality check."},{"time":964217,"text":"Where you have an expenditure of public money"},{"time":966563,"text":"and it is without accountability"},{"time":969518,"text":"and it's without transparency,"},{"time":971158,"text":"it will always be equal to corruption,"},{"time":973414,"text":"whether you're in Russia or Nigeria or Alaska,"},{"time":976619,"text":"it will always be equal to corruption, and that is what we are dealing with here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":980819,"text":"I'm going to continue the work"},{"time":983130,"text":"to press on, to get some resolution"},{"time":987476,"text":"of those matters at the Ministry of Finance."},{"time":989186,"text":"If it is I have to go to court personally, I will do that."},{"time":991738,"text":"We will continue to press on."},{"time":992926,"text":"We will continue to work within JCC."}]},{"cues":[{"time":994877,"text":"But I want to step back from the Trinidad and Tobago context"},{"time":997578,"text":"and bring something new to the table"},{"time":999497,"text":"in terms of an international example."},{"time":1001323,"text":"We had the journalist [Heather] Brooke speaking"},{"time":1004224,"text":"about her battle against government corruption,"},{"time":1006541,"text":"and she introduced me to this website, Alaveteli.com."},{"time":1011978,"text":"And Alaveteli.com is a way for us to have an open database"},{"time":1016648,"text":"for Freedom of Information applications,"},{"time":1019427,"text":"and speak with each other."},{"time":1021543,"text":"I could see what you're applying for."},{"time":1023780,"text":"You could see what I applied for and what replies I got."},{"time":1027312,"text":"We can work on it together. We need to build a collective database"},{"time":1030248,"text":"and a collective understanding of where we are to go to the next point."},{"time":1033552,"text":"We need to increase the consciousness."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1035192,"text":"The final thing I want to say is in relation to this one,"},{"time":1039246,"text":"which is a lovely website from India"},{"time":1041024,"text":"called IPaidABribe.com."},{"time":1043466,"text":"They have international branches,"},{"time":1045252,"text":"and it's important for us to tune into this one."},{"time":1047696,"text":"IPaidABribe.com is really important,"},{"time":1050152,"text":"a good one to log on to and see."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1052568,"text":"I'm going to pause there. I'm going to ask you for your courage."},{"time":1055195,"text":"Discard the first myth; it is a crime."},{"time":1057416,"text":"Discard the second myth; it is a big thing."},{"time":1059734,"text":"It's a huge problem. It's an economic crime."},{"time":1062232,"text":"And let us continue working together"},{"time":1064280,"text":"to betterment in this situation,"},{"time":1065747,"text":"stability and sustainability in our society. Thank you."}]}]}